<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Happy Anniversary Indahh</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Pacifico&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #f8cdda, #f88fa1);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .container {
      text-align: center;
      color: white;
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive;
      font-size: 3em;
      margin-bottom: 0.2em;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .btn {
      margin-top: 2em;
      padding: 10px 25px;
      font-size: 1em;
      background: white;
      color: #f06292;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background: #f06292;
      color: white;
    }
    .hearts {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hearts span {
      position: absolute;
      display: block;
      color: white;
      animation: float 10s linear infinite;
    }
    @keyframes float {
      0% {
        transform: translateY(100vh) scale(0);
        opacity: 1;
      }
      100% {
        transform: translateY(-10vh) scale(1.5);
        opacity: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Happy Anniversary Indahh</h1>
    <p>Aku bersyukur banget bisa punya kamu. Terima kasih udah jadi bagian terindah dalam hidupku. Semoga cinta kita selalu tumbuh dan langgeng sampai tua nanti.</p>
    <button class="btn" onclick="alert('Aku cinta kamu lebih dari kata-kata bisa ungkapkan.')">Klik ini, Sayang!</button>
  </div>
  <div class="hearts">
    <span style="left:10%; font-size:20px">❤️</span>
    <span style="left:20%; font-size:25px">❤️</span>
    <span style="left:30%; font-size:18px">❤️</span>
    <span style="left:40%; font-size:22px">❤️</span>
    <span style="left:50%; font-size:24px">❤️</span>
    <span style="left:60%; font-size:19px">❤️</span>
    <span style="left:70%; font-size:23px">❤️</span>
    <span style="left:80%; font-size:21px">❤️</span>
    <span style="left:90%; font-size:20px">❤️</span>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
